{"tid":1571321,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"中共如何控制香港","createTime":"2019-09-15T11:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T17:53:43.000Z","uid":276971,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"48153a543c77ce5d16767341db0e9fc6f8a981e1","tid":1571321,"uid":276971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:45:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9qI-7UBlrkc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9qI-7UBlrkc&d=02TnLe2cOfQrY9jdqtoXeQRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=1c021f3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9qI-7UBlrkc</a>"},{"pid":"3a44ebfa53e675678ab75ab8491154096f4768a8","tid":1571321,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48153a543c77ce5d16767341db0e9fc6f8a981e1","tid":1571321,"uid":276971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:45:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9qI-7UBlrkc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9qI-7UBlrkc&d=02TnLe2cOfQrY9jdqtoXeQRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=1c021f3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9qI-7UBlrkc</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:53:43.000Z","msg":"（重要）大家千祈唔好做以下的事<br />\n1.不要捐款支持連登登報慶祝國慶<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/g20celebratemotherbirthday/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fg20celebratemotherbirthday%2F&d=02TnLe2cOfQrY9jdqtoXeQRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=f9fe6038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/g20celebratemotherbirthday/</a><br />\n，不要有錢出錢，不要有力出力（share,推）<br />\n2.不要塗污紙幣，在上面寫口號，這是違法的，而且浪費紙張和墨水，不環保，尤其不要塗污港幣和人民幣，這是有辱國體的<br />\n3.不要去藍絲商戶集體排隊齋坐借廁所無幫襯，這會影響他們生計的<br />\n4.不要以貼紙來張貼連儂牆，因為貼紙既放防水又難撕，這會另藍絲搣到發脾氣兼指甲都披埋，很可憐的<br />\n麻煩大家幫手推<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1572232/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1572232/page/1</a>"}]}